file_insights.primary_purpose: Create guidelines table for RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) pipeline

patterns_discovered: Vector database design for semantic search
Postgres with pgvector extension for embedding storage
HNSW indexing for fast cosine similarity search
Row Level Security (RLS) policies for access control
gotchas_discovered: Vector dimension hardcoded to 1536 (specific to text-embedding-3-small)
Cosine similarity search implemented via distance metric
Metadata stored as flexible JSONB for extensibility

approach_outcome.description: Added content and metadata columns to guidelines table
key_additions: Created guidelines table with embedding support

recommendations: Add more granular RLS policies if needed
Implement periodic index maintenance for HNSW index
Add validation for metadata JSON structure
